        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "When trying to use an external host like this:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nresources.db.adapter               = PDO_MYSQL\r\nresourses.db.params.host           = \"mysql51-48.pro\"\r\nresources.db.params.username       = \"XXXXXX\"\r\nresources.db.params.password       = \"XXXXXX\"\r\nresources.db.params.dbname         = \"XXXXXX\"\r\nresources.db.isDefaultTableAdapter = true\r\nresources.db.params.charset        = \"utf8\"\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThe resulting dsn generated by {{Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_Abstract::_dsn()}} does not contain the host value has it is not passed to it in the config object.\r\nThus it is not possible to connect to any database whose not localhost.\r\n\r\nAdding manually the host in the function make the connection works has it should."
        },
