                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=anthor",
                        "name": "anthor",
                        "displayName": "Anthor",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Well I wonder where the host is going in a reel application as when I do some var_dump, \r\nespecially in {{Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_Abstract::_dsn()}} and {{Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract::__construct}}, \r\nnone of the two get a host key.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=anthor",
                        "name": "anthor",
                        "displayName": "Anthor",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2013-03-20T15:36:04.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2013-03-20T15:36:04.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/53378",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=frosch",
                        "name": "frosch",
                        "displayName": "Frank Br\u00fcckner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Please add quotation marks for adapter entry:\r\n{code}resources.db.adapter = \"pdo_mysql\"{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=frosch",
                        "name": "frosch",
                        "displayName": "Frank Br\u00fcckner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2013-03-20T15:49:01.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2013-03-20T15:49:01.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/53379",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=anthor",
                        "name": "anthor",
                        "displayName": "Anthor",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I just try that and get the exact same error.\r\nMySQL Error 2002, can't connect to localhost with socket.\r\n\r\n{{var_dump}} on the dsn produced by {{Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_Abstract::dsn()}} shows that no host is passed to the adapter, thus it's trying to connect the application to localhost..\r\n\r\nI'll try to reproduce it on a fresh application, but I can't see anything who would remove that config, as I can get it from my config object, and I'm not modifying the bootstrap DB.\r\n\r\nConfig was paste directly so I don't think my initialisation is wrong.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=anthor",
                        "name": "anthor",
                        "displayName": "Anthor",
                        "active": true
